item.title: Complier
item.dc:creator: @eddyauto13 eddyauto13
item.description:
@eddyauto13 wrote:

it seems everyone is having this problem i have just sorted it out though you right click the signlink.class file and then press read only so that it is “ON” then compile it will say access denied then right click signlink.class again and click read only again so it is “OFF” then compile and the problem should be fixed hope this helps
